    <p>We thank Mr Gary Ng Jit Meng for his feed­back (Wills Registry should hold soft copies of wills, July 27).</p>
    <p>The Sin­ga­pore Academy of Law has plans to add other re­lated func­tions to the Wills Registry, in­clud­ing a repos­i­tory for copies of wills as sug­gested by Mr Ng.</p>
    <p>These ser­vices will be rolled out pro­gres­sively over the next year.</p>


